Text:
If you haven't seen these videos then you owe it to yourself to download and watch them - the information they contain is truly astonishing.

As follow up, or maybe before even watching these, I'd recommend downloading torrents related to the 'Disclosure Project' - can be got here:

https://thepiratebay.org/search/disclosure%20project/0/99/200

Many thanks to the uploader.

Can also try the following for other energy stuff related to Steven Greer:
https://thepiratebay.org/search/steven%20greer/0/99/0
